---
import SiteLayout from "@layouts/SiteLayout.astro"
import Link from "@components/Link.astro"
---

<SiteLayout>
  <h3 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Keyboard Layout</h3>

  <!-- Avoid extra whitespace from formatter adding line breaks. -->
  <!-- https://github.com/withastro/prettier-plugin-astro/issues/353 -->
  <!-- prettier-ignore -->
  <p class="mb-4 text-slate-400">
    In service of my arm and wrist health, I type on a <Link href="https://kinesis-ergo.com/keyboards/advantage360/">Kinesis Advantage360 Pro</Link>
    and customize my keymap with <Link href="https://zmk.dev/">ZMK</Link>. Here is my current layout, drawn with
    <Link href="https://github.com/caksoylar/keymap-drawer">keymap-drawer</Link>.
    This image automatically updates whenever I make a change to the layout and rebuild the firmware!
  </p>

  <div class="rounded-xl bg-neutral-200">
    <img
      src="https://github.com/debashisbiswas/Adv360-Pro-ZMK/blob/V3.0/keymap-drawer/adv360.svg?raw=true"
      alt="Current keyboard layout"
    />
  </div>
</SiteLayout>
